### 获取产品列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/products?page=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc

### 获取产品详情
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/products/1

### 创建产品 - 原材料
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "RM-001",
  "name": "测试原材料",
  "type": "RAW_MATERIAL",
  "image": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
  "referencePurchasePrice": 100.50
}

### 创建产品 - 成品（带BOM）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "FP-001",
  "name": "测试成品",
  "type": "FINISHED_PRODUCT",
  "image": "https://example.com/image2.jpg",
  "guidancePrice": 299.99,
  "bomItems": [
    {
      "componentId": "1",
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "componentId": "2",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 更新产品
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "RM-001-UPDATED",
  "name": "更新后的原材料",
  "image": "https://example.com/updated-image.jpg",
  "referencePurchasePrice": 120.75
}

### 删除产品
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/products/3
